					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->Does how much you sleep affect your heart?&nbsp;According to&nbsp;health officials, adults who sleep fewer than seven hours each night are more likely to experience health problems. Dr. Juan Cardenas Rosales, an internal medicine physician at Mayo Clinic, stresses that adequate sleep is crucial for your overall well-being, including your heart health. Watch: The Mayo Clinic […]<p></p>
